314
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:31,610
It's fine.

315
00:22:31,610 --> 00:22:34,650
Are the students in the club doing well?

316
00:22:34,650 --> 00:22:37,230
They're much better than when they first started.

317
00:22:37,230 --> 00:22:39,660
They're passionate too.

318
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:42,110
