You should come by more often.

342
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:29,100
I got so curious when I heard that my son had a girlfriend.

343
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,650
We broke up.

344
00:24:34,650 --> 00:24:36,430
What?

345
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,920
I see.

346
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:45,690
I made a mistake.

347
00:24:46,290 --> 00:24:47,470
It's all right.

348
00:24:47,470 --> 00:24:51,410
Well, people break up and get back together at your age.

349
00:24:51,410 --> 00:24:53,880
That's how things are, right?

