00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:02,690
Yes.

362
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:03,850
I'm home.

363
00:27:03,850 --> 00:27:05,900
You're here.

364
00:27:10,870 --> 00:27:12,710
When did you get here?

365
00:27:16,020 --> 00:27:18,100
You should get home early.

