Me, neither.

370
00:27:35,150 --> 00:27:38,290
I think he's earlier than usual today.

371
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:53,320
 They asked me to do it. 

372
00:27:53,320 --> 00:27:56,510
 I said I wouldn't. 

373
00:27:56,510 --> 00:28:00,280
 The writer asked me just to do two lines. 

374
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:04,730
Here's my little brother with the complicated love life.

375
00:28:04,730 --> 00:28:06,370
What are you talking about?

376
00:28:07,680 --> 00:28:10,590
What's going on?

377
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:14,690
I thought you liked Ji Won, but your girlfriend is Seo Young.

378
00:28:14,690 --> 00:28:17,820
And then you broke up with her not long after.

379
00:28:19,380 --> 00:28:23,290
It's complicated, so I'm figuring it out one step at a time.

380
00:28:23,290 --> 00:28:24,370
Okay?

381
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:26,740
Well, well...

382
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:32,140
I heard you met the lawyer this afternoon.

383
00:28:32,140 --> 00:28:33,990
What did he say?

384
00:28:35,350 --> 00:28:38,320
Chief Lee keeps going out of his way.

385
00:28:39,470 --> 00:28:41,300
Your teacher, Mr. Lee,

386
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:44,390
he visited the lawyer first.

387
00:28:44,390 --> 00:28:48,940
I think he's meeting up with the people he used to work with.

388
00:28:48,940 --> 00:28:51,030
I see.

389
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:55,040
But I really wish he wouldn't.

390
00:28:56,440 --> 00:29:01,110
My homeroom teacher back in school helped me a lot with the trial until recently,

391
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:05,540
but eventually, he ended things badly with the school.

392
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:09,580
I'm worried the same thing will happen to Chief Lee.

393
00:29:11,280 --> 00:29:13,480
Is that what happened?

394
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:15,890
Yes.

395
00:29:15,890 --> 00:29:19,930
So don't pressure Chief Lee.

396
00:29:19,930 --> 00:29:23,860
We shouldn't burden others just for our sake.

